commentTextItems.html: full, on leg, Muruma runs down the track, punches this to the left of mid wicket and came back for the third run.

commentPostTextItems.html: Zimbabwe takes comfortably the first ODI by 7 wickets. Though the openers started slow, Ervine and Chakabva cruised through the chase comfortable before both losing their wickets at the end.
T Chatara is the man of the match for his 3 for 25 in his 10. That will be all for today, see you on friday for the second match. Cheers

commentTextItems.html: full, on leg, Maruma leans forwar and drives to long on

stories.seoTitle: UAE coach Dougie Brown makes adapting to conditions a priority for rest of series
